{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_04_01",
  "title": "兵藤雫 1話 かっこ良くなりたい…！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……相談がある……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san… I have something to discuss…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "深刻そうな雰囲気だな。一体どうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem pretty serious. What's going on?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "私はアイドルが好き……\nアイドルの知識なら誰にも負けない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I love idols…\nThere's no one who knows more about idols than me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "だから、トリエルとリズノワが移籍して来た時……\n凄くワクワクした……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ when TRINITYAiLE and LizNoir transferred here…\nI was really excited…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと憧れてたから……最初は話すのも緊張した……\nでも、一緒に練習したり……ライブで共演したり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because I've admired them for so long…At first‚ even talking to them made me nervous…\nBut practicing together… performing together in live shows…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "憧れのアイドルと交流することで……\n私も成長出来た……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By interacting with the idols I admired…\nI was able to grow too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "つまり……私が言いたいのは、そういうこと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So… Thats what I wanted to say…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いや、どういうことかさっぱり分からないんだが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I have no idea what you're talking about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "私はアイドルオタク……\n有名なアイドルを見ると、ふわあああってなる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm an idol otaku…\nWhen I see famous idols‚ I get ehehehe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "だから、怖くて……とても緊張するけど……\n思い切って……話し掛けてみたい……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ even though it's scary… and I get really nervous…\nI want to try my best and talk to them…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "有名なアイドル？\nもしかして、スリクスと話したいのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Famous idols?\nAre you saying you want to talk to IIIX?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスは、圧倒的カリスマの三人が揃って結成した\nスーパーアイドルグループ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "IIIX is a super idol group formed by\nthree overwhelmingly charismatic members…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "パリコレにも出たトップモデルのfranさん\n中高生に人気でフォロワー200万人のkanaさん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The top model fran-san who walked in Paris Collection…\nThe high schoolers' favorite with 2 million followers‚ kana-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリ覇者のmihoさん\n三人のカリスマによる奇跡のドリームチーム……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The winner of NEXT VENUS Grand Prix‚ miho-san…\nA dream team of three charismatic members…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロとはいろいろあったけど……\nそれでも、凄いアイドルなのは変わらない……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There were various things with Hoshimi Pro.‚ but…\nEven so‚ they're still amazing idols…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "今も大人気のトップアイドル……話してみたい……！\nけど、恐れ多くて、声を掛けられない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're still top idols loved by many… I want to talk to them…!\nBut I'm afraid to do so… and it seems like",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "それに、サニピと仲良くするのは嫌みたいで\n怖いオーラが出てて……近寄りがたい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "they don't want to be close with Sunny Peace….\nThey give off a scary aura… and it's hard to approach…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……それなら、スリクスと雫の四人だけで\n話せる機会をセッティングしようか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… In that case‚ how about I set up an opportunity for you\nand the four members of IIIX to talk?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "ひぃ……待って……！　いきなりそれはハードル高過ぎ\nスリクスと三対一はドルオタの心臓がもたない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wa-Wait…! Hold on…! Just suddenly suggesting that is too high of a hurdle…\nFor a hardcore idol fan like me‚ it's too much to face three of them at once…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "もっと徐々に距離を詰めたい……\nまずはレッスンを見学する、とか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to gradually build a closer relationship…\nMaybe like observing their lessons first…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、レッスンを見学してもいいか聞いてみるよ\n許可してもらえるかは分からないが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ I'll try asking if you can observe a lesson.\nI can't guarantee they'll agree though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "それで十分\nよろしくお願いします……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's enough for me.\nThank you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_coast_noon",
      "startTime": 151.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "ふおおお……！\n星見プロのスタジオに、本物のスリクスがいる……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoaaa…!\nThe real IIIX is in the Hoshimi Pro. studio…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いてもおかしくないだろ？\nスリクスは星見プロ所属のアイドルなんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It wouldn't be strange‚ would it?\nAfter all‚ IIIX is under Hoshimi Pro. too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk019.m4a",
      "text": "あああぁ……生スリクス、かっこ良過ぎる……\nみんな尊い……一生推せる……待って無理しんどい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh…! Live IIIX‚ they're so cool…!\nEveryone's precious… support them for life… But‚ wait‚ impossible…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "落ち着け雫、どんどん語彙力がなくなってきてるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Calm down‚ Shizuku. Your vocabulary is disappearing rapidly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "しかし、こうして見ると、同じダンスレッスンでも\nサニピとはやり方がかなり違うな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ looking at them like this‚ even in the same dance lesson‚\nTheir approach is quite different from Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk020.m4a",
      "text": "うん……サニピは練習中でも、みんなで話し合う\n納得がいくまで何回でもやり直す……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… Sunny Peace discusses things together even during practice.\nThey redo it as many times as needed until everyone is satisfied…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk021.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスは……無駄なことはやらない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "IIIX‚ on the other hand… they don't waste time on unnecessary things…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk022.m4a",
      "text": "計算された完璧なパフォーマンスを……\n短時間で効率良く、集中して覚える",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A perfectly calculated performance…\nEfficiently memorized in a short amount of time with intense focus…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk023.m4a",
      "text": "だから動きに迷いがない……\n洗練されていて、研ぎ澄まされたかっこ良さ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So there's no hesitation in their movements…\nThey're refined‚ polished‚ and incredibly cool…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "洗練か……雫もそういうかっこ良さに憧れるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Refined‚ huh… Does that kind of coolness also attract Shizuku?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk024.m4a",
      "text": "うん、憧れる\nスリクスみたいにかっこ良くなりたい……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I admire it.\nI want to become as cool as IIIX…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "いい刺激になったみたいだな\nこれならあの話を進めてみてもいいか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seems like it's providing good inspiration for you.\nIn that case‚ would it be alright to move forward with that plan…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-szk025.m4a",
      "text": "何か、新しいお仕事なの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this about a new job…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "実はある企業から、アイドルのかっこ良さに\nフォーカスした広告のオファーが来ているんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ a company has offered us an advertisement\nthat focuses on the coolness of idols…",
        "id": ""
