      "startTime": 236.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "指名で莉央さんとfranさんは決まっているが\nもう一人、意外性のある人がほしいって言われていて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While Rio-san and fran-san are already picked‚\nThey're looking for one more person with an unexpected appeal…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "雫にとっては新境地になるが\n意欲があるなら挑戦してみないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It could be a new challenge for Shizuku‚\nWould you be interested in trying it out?",
        "id": ""
